text: Ribeirinha is a parish in the municipality of Angra do Heroísmo on the island of Terceira in the Azores. The population in 2011 was 2,684,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of 7.53 km².Eurostat ==References== Category:Parishes of Angra do Heroísmo
title: Ribeirinha (Angra do Heroísmo)
